          "reviewBody": "Das Universal Academy baaki schools ke comparison mein zyada balanced approach rakhta hai, jahan sirf marks par nahi balki overall development par bhi equal focus diya jata hai. Yahan ke teachers zyada approachable aur attentive hain, jo har student ki needs ko samajhkar guide karte hain. School ka environment positive, disciplined aur student-friendly hai, aur saath hi bachon ke spiritual growth par bhi dhyaan diya jata hai, jo unhe values aur inner confidence develop karne mein help karta hai. Overall, yeh school academics, personality aur spiritual growth ke liye ek better option feel hota hai compared to many others.",
          "publisher": {
