            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Main apne bachche ke liye ek aisa school dhoond raha tha jahan padhai ke saath sanskaar bhi milein, aur Das Universal Academy ne meri expectation se zyada diya.\n\nYahan teachers genuinely care karte hain aur har child par dhyaan dete hain. Mere child ka confidence aur interest in studies clearly improve hua hai.\n\nEk parent hone ke naate, mujhe yahan apne bachche ka future safe lagta hai.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
