            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Main Das Universal Academy ka student hoon aur honestly bolun to yahan ka experience kaafi acha raha hai. Maine yahan 8th se padhai start ki thi aur tab se leke ab tak teachers ne hamesha support kiya hai.\n\nSabse achi baat yeh hai ki yahan sirf books ka hi nahi, balki overall development pe bhi focus hota hai. Teachers friendly hain, doubt kabhi bhi pooch lo clear kar dete hain without any hesitation.\n\nEnvironment bhi kaafi positive hai, padhai ka proper atmosphere milta hai jisse focus bana rehta hai. Exams ke time pe extra support aur guidance milti hai jo kaafi helpful hoti hai.\n\nAgar kisi ko ek aisa school chahiye jahan padhai ke saath confidence aur personality bhi develop ho, to Das Universal Academy definitely ek achi choice hai.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
